# Archie API — manual test requests
# Requires the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) or VS Code's built-in HTTP support.
# Edit @baseUrl and @docsDir to match your local setup, then click "Send Request" above any request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@docsDir = c:/path/to/your/docs

### Ingest all markdown files in docs/
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "directory": "{{docsDir}}"
}

### Query — certifications
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What certifications should I pursue?"
}

### Query — career path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What should my career focus be over the next 5 years?"
}

### Query — skills to develop
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What technical skills should I prioritize developing?"
}
